Biography

2023 (Sophomore): Played in eight games … Recorded seven tackles on the season, including five solo stops … Recovered a fumble which he returned for a touchdown … Also broke up a pass … Had a season-high two tackles three times (at UL Monroe, at Houston Christian and against No. 8 UIW) … His two tackles against the Cardinals were both solo stops … He also broke up a pass at HCU … Recovered a fumble on his own 40-yard line and returned it 60 yards for a touchdown which turned out to be the different in the game.

Junior College: Lettered as a freshman on the football team at Trinity Valley … Played in 10 games for the Cardinals during his rookie season … Picked off one pass.

High School: Helped lead Tompkins to a 2020 19-6A district title … Two-time all-district selection receiving recognition on both sides of the ball.
